snippet.title: Teller's Duty - Wishlist On Steam
snippet.description:
Teller’s Duty is a game that blends absurd satire about banking bureaucracy with time management gameplay. Featuring a vintage paper art style, it presents hilarious and unpredictable challenges while combining banking simulation, moral dilemmas, and dystopian storytelling. Every decision impacts survival, job security, creating a conspiracy-filled experience.

Wishlist Teller's Duty On Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3428570/Tellers_Duty/

Developed by: Hiscory Studio
Music used: The invention rooms by Savfk - www.youtube.com/@SavfkMusic
